info.author: Lars Heuer
info.description:
Package which supports deserialization of the Compact Topic Maps (CTM) syntax.

This package can be used to add a `CTM 1.0 <http://www.isotopicmaps.org/ctm/>`_
reader to the `tm <http://pypi.python.org/pypi/tm>`_ package.
info.name: tm.reader.ctm
info.summary: Compact Topic Maps (CTM) reader for the Topic Maps package
